1
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:18,960
Greetings, Right Wise King.

2
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:21,020
Now that Prince Ling has passed away,

3
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:23,160
the two of us have come to pledge our allegiance.

4
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,240
I hope you, Right Wise King,

5
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:26,320
